      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But now the kingdom to us has been shown,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is no less than our Jesus alone."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is the Person of Christ in us all,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And it begins as a seed when we call."
            }
          ]
